title: WHY RENT WHEN YOU CAN OWN? AFFORDABLE AND GREAT PRICES!! CALL US NOW!!
posting_body: ['NEW HOME FOR SALE AVAILABLE NOW FOR ONLY $58,300!!!', "Welcome to Three Crowns Senior Community where you'll get to experience a modern and secluded style of living.", 'Take joy in the tranquility, quality, and spaciousness of our homes.', 'We offer two bedroom homes on the convenient area of Las Vegas.', 'Our wonderful pet-friendly homes have plenty to offer our residents.', 'Take a dip in our year round, sparkling swimming pools or bring your loved ones to our Picnic Area / Pavilion equipped with BBQ’s and all of your picnic needs!', 'Come to Three Crowns and enjoy peace and comfort without giving up affordability.', 'Call today or stop by for a personal guided tour with us.', 'Community Amenities', '- Refreshing Pool', '- Beautiful Landscape', '- Laundry Facilities', '- Fitness Center', '- Billiards Room', '- Library', '- Clubhouse', '- RV Storage', '- Picnic Area / Pavilion / Grill', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- After Hours Patrol', '- On-Site Management', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Service', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats & dogs allowed.', 'Restrictions/fees apply.', 'Please contact us for more info', 'Space rent; $772.00', 'Trash; $8.65', 'Sewer; $22.52', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 8:00AM-5:00PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-2:00PM']
